بسملہ ار رحمان ار رحیم
The blessed names of Allah s.w.t
Listening or reciting or invoking in prayers using these names is very powerful.
If anyone suffering from illness or disease or jinn possession then they must Read or listen to the 99 names, it will surely by Allah's will grant them cure and tranquility.
